{"tid":107943,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講親咩都話讀完書先講","createTime":"2017-02-04T19:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T08:06:22.000Z","uid":56795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9413f75b9a72c556173b8f2794459492cd3bf922","tid":107943,"uid":56795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:20:04.000Z","msg":"真係每次同爸媽傾計 <br />\n唔係每次 間唔中會發生<br />\n本身都傾得好地地<br />\n講下自己將來有咩想做<br />\n有咩想買之類 計劃可能會去邊<br />\n好多時候都只係諗下 純粹想傾下 <br />\n講下比佢地知自己諗咩<br />\n之後個回應次次都係 「讀書完先講」<br />\n真係好掃興<br />\n已經無咩心情繼續傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果咁咩都唔洗講啦 屋企自閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時又話咩都唔同佢地傾 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係莫名其妙<br />\n<br />\n呻完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無巴絲有相似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d457c1d4ede9b5e0182e2f175b98136aa84c950","tid":107943,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係每次同爸媽傾計 <br />\n唔係每次 間唔中會發生<br />\n本身都傾得好地地<br />\n講下自己將來有咩想做<br />\n有咩想買之類 計劃可能會去邊<br />\n好多時候都只係諗下 純粹想傾下 <br />\n講下比佢地知自己諗咩<br />\n之後個回應次次都係 「讀書完先講」<br />\n真係好掃興<br />\n已經無咩心情繼續傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果咁咩都唔洗講啦 屋企自閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時又話咩都唔同佢地傾 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係莫名其妙<br />\n<br />\n呻完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無巴絲有相似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相反 對我好大期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d35531f44aa2d505c91631aa6b25e650f2c55b","tid":107943,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d892eccccbe45a4670f99c647d3edfba04ff2b","tid":107943,"uid":56795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote></blockquote><br />\n相反 對我好大期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n佢地都會 比較下人地同我<br />\n但我係講下閒聊都要提讀書<br />\n其實讀書就一定<br />\n唔通心每分每刻都諗讀書<br />\n唔可以講想將來有咩想去做咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20682c171e959a81109bfa7c071d7d83d1b928e2","tid":107943,"uid":56795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b958c8e2ed7d95976e398f0edfd8c8d342437367","tid":107943,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"我已經行左出呢個stage,記住，唔好理佢地點講。認為岩就做"},{"pid":"54ac6c99b5ed3b317ef4b9d4e7c53c2738adf2da","tid":107943,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"咪又係錢"},{"pid":"120299ce7b5638cf9b7e7d003d3c6909010652fd","tid":107943,"uid":56795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪又係錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如 <br />\n我話 我想之後去working holiday <br />\n會答 讀完書先講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}